Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=12}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, Paulie!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.71,0:01:55.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Today, I'm definitely not gonna let you get away! - OG}Dessa vez você não vai escapar!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.21,0:01:57.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm saying, wait a bit longer! - OG}E {\i1}eu{\i0} tô pedindo pra esperar mais um pouco!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é aquele?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele é o Paulie.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's being chased by debt collectors again. - OG}Ele tá fugindo dos cobradores de novo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.51,0:02:04.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Paga o dinheiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.01,0:02:07.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Like I said, I don't have money today. - OG}Já disse, não tenho grana hoje!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.39,0:02:10.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é desculpa!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're really persistent! - OG}Droga, eles não desistem!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Huh? This is perfect! I see yagara bulls! - OG}Hã? Perfeito! Touros yagara!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rope Action!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.41,0:02:23.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's one of the shipwrights at Galley-La! - OG}Ele é um carpinteiro naval da Galley-La!{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.87,0:02:29.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa, mas eu vou pegar emprestado\Num dos seus yagaras por um instante!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Round Turn!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! He got away again! - OG}Droga! Ele escapou de novo!{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, então pessoal, se cuidem!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.79,0:03:03.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's run together again! - OG}Vamos correr juntos de novo em breve!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.45,0:03:10.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Seriously... you came\Nat just the right time! - OG}Sério mesmo! Vocês chegaram\Nna hora certa!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.40,0:03:17.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que alívio! Ele é um dos\Nseus carpinteiros, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Valeu!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele dinheiro é nosso!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Dinheiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, this... - OG}Deixa eu ver...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.81,0:03:35.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hello...! Hm... Hey! - OG}Ei...! Hã? Ei!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come back here! - OG}Volta aqui!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That son of a bitch! - OG}Aquele desgraçado!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna catch him–! Huh? - OG}Eu vou trazer ele de vol– Hã?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll go. - OG}Deixa comigo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.66,0:03:47.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Um... Um pombo?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai, ai, ai, ai! Ei, ei, me solta!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos você tá fazendo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.08,0:03:57.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't run! I'm saying I got it, aren't I?! - OG}{I won't run away again, man! I get it, okay?! - Z}Eu não vou fugir, cara! Já entendi, tá?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Solta a minha orelha!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.78,0:04:03.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Here I was lucky enough to find\Na lot of money and now...! - OG}Justo agora que eu tive a sorte\Nde achar toda essa grana...!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Você vai se arrepender, Lucci!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.93,0:04:09.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't pay back your debts\Nwith someone else's money, you fool! - OG}Não pague suas dívidas com\No dinheiro dos outros, seu imbecil!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I found found this money! - OG}Mas eu {\i1}achei{\i0} esse dinheiro!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're still saying that?! Coo coo! - OG}Você acha que essa história cola?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só por acaso estava no yagara\Nque eu peguei emprestado!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles voltaram.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, fico feliz por você, Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.87,0:04:26.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You talk like it was someone else's problem!\NIt's our 200 millino belly! - OG}Não fala como se não fosse problema seu!\NSão os {\i1}nossos{\i0} 200 milhões de belly!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.71,0:04:32.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso aí! Por que diabos {\i1}você{\i0}\Nnão foi o primeiro a ir buscar?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas o pombo disse que ia.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom... Me desculpe.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please let us take care of our idiot coworker, - OG}Melhor a gente lidar com\Nnosso colega idiota...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{as if you guys were to capture him,\Nit would create bitter feelings. - OG}senão, ia criar um clima\Nruim se vocês pegassem ele.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.90,0:04:48.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, please excuse him. Consider it good\Nthat the money wasn't stolen by the Franky Family. - OG}Bom, considerem-se sortudos de o dinheiro\Nnão ter sido roubado pela Família Franky.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hmm... É verdade, mas...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, é verdade, é verdade.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.23,0:04:59.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Say... who were those\Nweird-looking guys earlier? - OG}E aí, quem eram aqueles\Ncaras esquisitos de antes?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.07,0:05:02.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Franky Family is\Na group of ship demolition workers. - OG}A Família Franky é um grupo\Nde desmontadores de navios.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.40,0:05:07.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Demolition workers? They didn't look\Nlike such decent craftsmen, though. - OG}Desmontadores? Pareciam mais\Nbandidos do que artesãos honestos.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.37,0:05:11.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É. Eles também são caçadores de recompensa por fora.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.60,0:05:16.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Every time they find pirates coming\Nthrough this city, they cause quarrels. - oG}Eles fazem um baita estrago toda vez\Nque descobrem piratas na cidade.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São uma praga pública.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.83,0:05:23.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If they crush the pirates who come to our town,\Nthey can take their ship, too, right? - OG}Se eles derrubam os piratas que vêm\Npra cidade, também ficam com o navio, sacou?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.38,0:05:26.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They demolish the ship\Nand sell the usable lumber. - OG}Desmontam o navio e vendem\Na madeira aproveitável.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's how their business works. - OG}É assim que o negócio da Família Franky funciona.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.89,0:05:34.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How bad-natured...! Are they trying to completely wipe the pirate groups out? - OG}Que absurdo! Eles querem acabar\Ncom {\i1}todos{\i0} os grupos piratas?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.06,0:05:37.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Um, if you become their victims,\Nnot even your bones will remain. - OG}Bom, se vocês caírem nas mãos deles,\Nnão vai sobrar nem os ossos.{Z - thrown back in the faces of the Franky Family in Water Seven 4 at 08:31}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eles não pareciam tão fortes.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're just underlings. - OG}Aqueles são só capangas.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.84,0:05:48.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whatever you do, don't underestimate\Nthe family's boss, Franky, who's behind them. - OG}Pensem o que quiserem deles, mas nunca\Nsubestimem o chefe deles, o Franky.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.45,0:05:54.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We brought him over, Iceburg-san. - OG}Trouxemos ele, Sr. Iceburg.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.01,0:05:56.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're doing it again\NYou're hurting my ear! - OG}De novo, tá machucando minha orelha!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thanks, Lucci. - OG}Bom trabalho, Lucci.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.71,0:06:01.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{We're sorry that that idiot\Ncaused you trouble. - OG}Desculpa por esse imbecil ter causado problemas.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ah! He spoke again! - OG}Ah! Ele falou de novo!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Coo coo!}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora peça desculpas pra eles, Paulie!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That pigeon is doing all the talking! - OG}O pombo tá falando por todo mundo!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's as if he's speaking\Nfor that man with a hat. - OG}Parece que ele fala pelo cara de chapéu.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.72,0:06:17.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In any case, I'm glad we got the money back. - OG}De qualquer forma, que bom que o dinheiro voltou!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you're the owner of the money? - OG}Ei, então o dinheiro era de vocês?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I picked it up for you. - OG}Eu trouxe de volta pra vocês.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, valeu!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.69,0:06:26.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you wanna thank me, then give me 10%. - OG}Se quer agradecer, me dá dez por cento.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, mister. - OG}Desculpa aí, senhor.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.10,0:06:38.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This guy racked up a gambling debt, so he's greedy and has no manners. - OG}A dívida de jogo desse cara é tão alta\Nque ele ficou ganancioso e sem educação.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So, why the heck are you talking?! - OG}Tá, mas por que você tá falando?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.63,0:06:43.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You bastard! You're really running your mouth, Lucci! - OG}Seu safado! Para de ficar\Nabrindo a boca, Lucci!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't take it anymore! - OG}Já passou dos limites!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rope Action:
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Coo coo!}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bowline Knot!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Punishment}{That's a paddlin'!}{...}Discipline:
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ahh...}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Não, não! Ele tá falando sério!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Pole-and-Line Fishing! - OG}{Hook, Line, and Sinker! - Viz}Fly Fishing!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ele tá bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... it's nothing new. - OG}Bom, isso sempre acontece.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! O-O-Olha aquilo!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.67,0:07:27.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's parried that impact with just one arm! - OG}Ele absorveu o impacto com um braço só!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His fingers are sinking into the ground. - OG}{Each finger penetrated the hard ground! - Z}Os dedos dele afundaram no chão!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.28,0:07:36.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What the heck kind of fingers does he have? - OG}{Wh-What the heck is up with his fingers? - Z}Q-Que tipo de dedos esse cara tem?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.35,0:07:40.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's with the shipwrights working here? - OG}Que tipo de carpinteiros navais\Ntrabalham aqui?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Você aí, de óculos!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pensa bem.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.61,0:07:52.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The one who mocked\Nor provoked you was... - OG}O único que zombou\Nou provocou você{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,foi o pombo!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.19,0:08:00.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's fine! - OG}Tá, mas...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.75,0:08:04.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The one who hit me was Lucci! - OG}Quem me bateu foi o Lucci!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.25,0:08:08.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The pigeon can't hit you himself,\Nso he had that guy hit you! - OG}O pombo não pode te bater sozinho,\Nentão mandou aquele cara fazer!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pombo!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.38,0:08:14.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you wanna fight, fight yourself! - OG}Luta suas próprias lutas!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fala alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Coo coo!}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh? Quer brigar?\NVem pra cá, seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para com isso, Paulie.
Comment: 5,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Coo coo. Well, sorry for the fuss.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, desculpa pela confusão.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.82,0:08:35.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Rob L– N-Não, quer dizer, Hattori o pombo.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.18,0:08:40.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And this is Rob Lucci. He works here. Nice to meet you. Coo coo! - OG}E esse aqui é o Rob Lucci, um dos\Ntrabalhadores daqui. Prazer em conhecê-los!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.24,0:08:44.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh? He almost introduced\Nhimself as if he were human! - OG}Oh? Ele quase se apresentou\Ncomo se {\i1}ele{\i0} fosse o humano!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Aha! Yeah, I got it! That's ventriloquism, isn't it?! - OG}Ahá! Já sei o truque!\NIsso é ventriloquismo, né?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! Seriously?! Then it was\Nyou who was complaining! - OG}Uau! Sério?! Então era você\Nque {\i1}tava{\i0} provocando ele!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.31,0:08:54.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é muito bom! Eu nem percebi!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.49,0:08:57.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop it. It's no big deal. Coo coo. - OG}Para. Não é nada demais.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.00,0:09:02.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's a weirdo who can't talk\Nto people properly. - OG}Ele é um esquisitão que não consegue\Nfalar com as pessoas normalmente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.81,0:09:08.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait a sec! What's with that woman?! - OG}Espera aí! O que é isso, moça?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What? - OG}Quem... eu?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're shameless! - OG}Que sem-vergonha!{WF}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.38,0:09:18.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're showing your legs too much! - OG}Você tá mostrando as pernas demais!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.20,0:09:22.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a workplace for men!\NLook how you're dressed! - OG}Aqui é um local de trabalho pra homens!\NO que te deu na cabeça pra se vestir assim?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Calma, Paulie, se acalma.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você também, Kalifa!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.72,0:09:35.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You haven't learned your lesson\Nand are wearing such outrageous clothes again! - OG}Você deveria saber que não pode\Nusar roupas escandalosas assim!{Z - CPS}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.41,0:09:39.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quantas vezes eu tenho que falar?!\NUsa calça! Calça {\i1}comprida{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que cara mais doido...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Calça comprida?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele também é esquisito!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.81,0:09:48.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, that's it. Let's open the door\Nand go inside already. - OG}Bom, chega disso. Vamos abrir\No portão e entrar de uma vez.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.70,0:10:05.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At any rate, what a huge door!\NAnd this requires manual operation? - OG}Inacreditável o tamanho desse portão!\NE ele é operado manualmente?!{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqueles dois esquisitões conseguem abrir sozinhos?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Tá mexendo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.29,0:10:16.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, cada doca tem apenas\Ncinco encarregados carpinteiros.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.28,0:10:20.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They may not look like it, but their skills made them foremen at Dock 1. - OG}Estranhos como são, a habilidade deles garantiu\Nos cargos de encarregado na Doca Um.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kaku, who we talked about earlier,\Nis one of them, too. - OG}O Kaku, o cara de antes, é um deles.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a world where craftsmen's\Nskills are all that matters. - OG}O que importa nesse mundo\Né a habilidade do artesão.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if their personalities are weird,\Ndon't worry about it. - OG}Eles são esquisitos, mas e daí?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, they're weird. - OG}É, eles {\i1}são{\i0} esquisitos mesmo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ah, the door's started opening. - OG}Ah! Tá começando a abrir!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.57,0:10:36.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't let the money leave your hands.\NI don't think we have thieves inside, but... - OG}E segurem firme o dinheiro de vocês.\NNão deve ter ladrões aqui dentro, mas...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.90,0:10:42.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, it was also my fault earlier,\Nand it caused you trouble, too. - OG}Bom, a culpa também foi minha.\NDesculpa pelo transtorno.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.16,0:10:43.66,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Garante que vai me proteger direitinho!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, got it! Leave it to me! - OG}Tá, pode deixar! Deixa comigo!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô preocupada.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.29,0:10:49.96,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.96,0:10:54.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This Dock 1 comprises\Nthe main force of the Galley-La Company, - OG}O que vocês veem aqui é a Doca Um,\No centro da Galley-La Company,{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and it undertakes the most difficult work. - OG}onde lidamos com as encomendas mais difíceis.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Venham, entrem.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.15,0:11:01.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Uau!\N– Uau!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.40,0:11:17.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whooa! Huge! - OG}Uau! É tudo enorme!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.49,0:11:22.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A shipyard has a tremendous impact\Nwhen seen up close! - OG}Esse estaleiro é ainda mais incrível\Nvisto de perto!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.41,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,É mesmo!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.10,0:11:28.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh? They're building a huge galleon!\NWhose is that? - OG}Oh? Estão construindo um galeão\Nenorme! Pra quem é?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's full of craftsmen. - OG}Tem tantos artesãos aqui.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Venham! Por aqui.{OG}{Come! This way. - Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}Oh, é o Sr. Iceburg!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! O chefe tá aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Good morning, Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}Bom dia, Sr. Iceburg!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom dia!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Boss! Could you take a look \Nat how the outer panels turned out? - OG}Chefe! Pode dar uma olhada\Nem como ficou o casco?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Claro! Passo aí depois!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Good day, Iceburg-san! - OG}Belo dia, Sr. Iceburg!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... Hello, are things going well? - OG}Bom, olá. Tudo indo bem?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor! Tudo muito bem!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.36,0:12:01.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! Ice pops is quite popular. - OG}Uau! Todo mundo gosta do Icechefe.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.46,0:12:04.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Of course he is. In this city,\Nskills are all that matters. - OG}Claro que sim. Habilidade é\Ntudo nessa cidade.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.23,0:12:09.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{On this island, shipbuilding\Nwas well-developed from the start, - OG}A construção naval sempre foi\Na principal indústria dessa ilha,{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and seven shipbuilding companies\Nwere competing with each other. - OG}e sete estaleiros competiam\Npelos contratos.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.22,0:12:17.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Meanwhile, he attracted craftsmen\Nwith his genius shipbuilding skills. - OG}Ele acabou encantando os carpinteiros\Ncom sua habilidade genial.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.54,0:12:22.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then he put those seven companies together\Nto form a company five years ago. - OG}Cinco anos atrás, ele conseguiu fundir\Ntodas as sete companhias, e o resto é história.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And that's this Galley-La Company. - OG}Essa é a atual Galley-La Company.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His passion and skills\Nin shipbuilding have never changed, - OG}A paixão e habilidade dele pela\Nconstrução naval não diminuíram,{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the craftsmen won't forget\Ntheir respect towards him. - oG}e ele nunca perdeu o respeito\Ndos carpinteiros.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And, because the craftsmen\Nare proud of their skills, - OG}E, como os artesãos têm\Norgulho de suas habilidades,{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.90,0:12:38.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{they never give in to pirates or authority. - OG}eles não se curvam a piratas nem a autoridades.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is that kind of place. - OG}É assim que as coisas funcionam aqui.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.00,0:12:42.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? - OG}Quê...?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, pops. I heard that you're a top-notch shipwright. - OG}Ei, velhão. Ouvi dizer que você é\Num carpinteiro naval de primeira.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you wanna be a pirate with me? - OG}Quer ser pirata comigo?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What the hell are you saying,\Nyou son of a bitch?! - OG}Quer repetir isso, moleque?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.17,0:12:51.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{H-How insolent! - OG}Q-Que atrevimento!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, now... He's always like that. - OG}Calma, calma. Ele é sempre assim.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sorry about that. - OG}Desculpa aí.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.00,0:12:59.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... you guys don't even have a single shipwright? - OG}Bom... vocês não têm nenhum\Ncarpinteiro naval no navio?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.09,0:12:59.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.90,0:13:04.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We came to this island in order to have our ship repaired and to find a new crew member. - OG}Viemos pra essa ilha pra consertar\Nnosso navio e achar um novo tripulante.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's true that we have tons of shipwrights. - OG}É verdade que temos um monte\Nde carpinteiros navais,{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.40,0:13:10.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I wonder if anyone would\Nwant to go on board a pirate ship. - OG}mas não sei se algum deles quer virar pirata.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.47,0:13:14.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you find someone who wants to go\Nwith you, you can headhunt him. - OG}Se tiver alguém aqui disposto\Na navegar com vocês, é de vocês.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.23,0:13:19.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really?! You're generous!\NCan't I ask you to join us, pops? - OG}Sério?! Você é generoso demais!\NTem certeza que não quer vir, velhão?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.19,0:13:22.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... I can't. I'm the mayor. - OG}Bom, eu não posso. Sou o prefeito.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who cares?! - OG}E daí?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.67,0:13:30.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{By the way, is the woman named\NNico Robin really on board your ship? - OG}A propósito, tem mesmo uma mulher\Nchamada Nico Robin no navio de vocês?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, she is. - OG}Tem sim!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela é muito inteligente.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.79,0:13:39.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Tem algum problema com a Robin?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.26,0:13:40.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No... - OG}Não.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.72,0:13:48.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In any case, it's really amazing! - OG}Não consigo acreditar como isso é incrível!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.05,0:13:51.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Segura firme! Sem pressa! Vai devagar!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.35,0:13:56.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we could install a cannon like that,\Nthe Merry would also be... Hm? - OG}Se a gente instalasse um canhão desses,\Na {\i1}Merry{\i0} ficaria mais– Hã?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! A demi-culverin cannon! - OG}Uau! Uma demi-culverin!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.94,0:14:04.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How cool! It's so long...! And shining! - OG}Que demais! É tão comprido... e brilhante!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanna fire something like that, one time! - OG}Eu daria qualquer coisa pra atirar\Num desses pelo menos uma vez.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a good chance. - OG}Agora é nossa chance.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.61,0:14:13.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece ser feito de cobre.\NDeve ser bem caro!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que eles deixam eu experimentar atirar?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.08,0:14:20.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, espera. Agora a gente tem 300 milhões de belly.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.45,0:14:23.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We should be able to buy\None or more cannons like that! - OG}Dá pra comprar alguns desses canhões!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.78,0:14:35.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wasn't there someone there? - OG}Não tinha alguém ali?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Kaku!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você estava?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.54,0:14:51.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Numa avaliação.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Você é o cara de antes!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então você vistoriou nosso navio?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I did. - OG}É, dei uma boa olhada nele.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you were here, Iceburg-san. - OG}Ah, Sr. Iceburg, o senhor está aqui.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.08,0:15:02.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know the situation. How was it? - OG}Já estou por dentro. Como foi?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... - OG}Pra ser honesto...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! Come down now! - OG}Luffy! Desce daí!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.28,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! É verdade?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.90,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you're lying, you'll pay for it! - OG}Se for mentira, você vai pagar!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.00,0:15:33.57,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I never lie on the job. - OG}No meu trabalho, mentira não tem vez.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? Where's Usopp? - OG}E aí, cadê o Usopp?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.61,0:15:54.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He was wandering about over there up\Nuntil just a moment ago. - OG}Ele {\i1}tava{\i0} ali até agora pouco.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.51,0:16:01.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you guys!\NDon't these bags belong to you? - OG}Ei, vocês!\NEssas maletas não são de vocês?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ah! They're the bags Usopp was carrying! - OG}Ah! O Usopp tava carregando essas!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, são nossas.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Valeu!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.29,0:16:14.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... Where did Usopp go...\Nleaving our precious money alone?! - OG}Putz! Pra onde você foi, Usopp,\Nlargando todo o nosso dinheiro sozinho?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.74,0:16:15.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dinheiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É! Nessas maletas tem 200 milhões de belly.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,200 milhões de belly?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No way. See ya! - OG}Boa essa. Até mais!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Impossível.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So, how much does it look like it'll cost? - OG}Então, quanto vai custar?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente pode pagar o quanto for!\NTemos dinheiro de sobra!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.47,0:16:41.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se possível, eu quero que ela fique mais forte,\Ncom mais canhões e mais rápida!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.93,0:16:45.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can you also add pretty\Ndecorations on the outer panels? - OG}Dá pra estilizar o casco\Ncom uns entalhes bem bonitos?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can you renovate inside as well? - OG}Dá pra reformar o interior também?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, hold on a sec... - OG}Calma aí, pessoal.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.82,0:16:55.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've been having some\Ntremendous journeys, haven't you? - OG}Vocês têm passado por umas\Naventuras e tanto, não é?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah! We flew in the sky, and fell as well. - OG}E como! A gente voou pelo céu\Ne caiu lá de cima.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We climbed a mountain and got skewered. - OG}Subimos uma montanha de navio\Ne até fomos trespassados.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Passamos por muita coisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, a gente quer que ela seja bem consertada!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.39,0:17:09.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As cicatrizes de batalha dela são profundas demais.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.81,0:17:13.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you mean it'll take quite\Na long time to fix her? - OG}Quer dizer que vai demorar\Nmuito pra consertar?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.05,0:17:19.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Frankly speaking, your ship... - OG}Vou ser direto. O navio de vocês...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{can no longer be fixed, even with our skills. - OG}não pode mais ser consertado, nem com a nossa perícia.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is her keel damaged or something? - OG}Imagino que seja a quilha.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É. Ela sofreu muitos danos.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, no... - OG}Não pode ser.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.69,0:17:49.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas a gente veio navegando\Nnormalmente até hoje!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.92,0:17:54.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's suppose that we\Ndid what we could anyway. - OG}Vamos supor que a gente fizesse\No máximo possível.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.38,0:17:58.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The probability of her reaching the next island is... - OG}A probabilidade de ela chegar\Nna próxima ilha é...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.40,0:18:02.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,zero.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.21,0:18:18.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Merry... Can you really not... - OG}{\i1}Merry{\i0}, você realmente...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{sail anymore? - OG}não pode mais navegar?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Crap... - OG}Que droga.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.99,0:18:31.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Sanji. I got a little lost in the books. - OG}Desculpa, Sanji. Eu me perdi um pouco nos livros.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's nothing you should apologize about. - OG}Não precisa se desculpar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.50,0:18:39.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I just assumed that the one who was with Robin-chan was you in your human form. - OG}Eu só achei que quem tava com a Robin\Nera você na forma humana.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.49,0:18:44.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, quem era aquele homem mascarado?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In addition, it's strange\Nthat they suddenly disappeared. - OG}Mais estranho ainda, eles desapareceram de repente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.80,0:18:51.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah... Robin's scent disappeared there, too. - OG}É. O cheiro da Robin sumiu ali também.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I hope nothing bad happens...\NMy stomach's in a knot... - OG}Provavelmente não é nada,\Nmas tô com um frio na barriga.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.82,0:18:56.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? - OG}Hã?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you want me to take a look at you? - OG}Quer que eu te examine?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não tô doente!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.05,0:19:04.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This reminds me of what Aokiji said. - OG}Sinto que aquele tal de Aokiji\Nfalou algo sobre isso.{Z}{One frame fade - probably a mistake in the edit.}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did he say something worrisome? - OG}E o que ele disse?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He said stuff about Robin-chan's past, right? - OG}Ele ficou fazendo alusão ao passado da Robin.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.20,0:19:13.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And he said to us that we'd\Nsomeday regret taking her on. - OG}Ele também disse que um dia\Nnos arrependeríamos de acolhê-la.{Z}{Reference LRLL 06}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now that you mention it... - OG}Agora que você falou...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But does that have something to do\Nwith Robin's disappearance?! - OG}Mas o que isso tem a ver\Ncom o desaparecimento da Robin?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.33,0:19:21.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sei.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.00,0:19:25.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In any case, we're getting nowhere like this.\NLet's go back to the Merry for now. - OG}De qualquer forma, assim não vamos a lugar nenhum.\NVamos voltar pra {\i1}Merry{\i0} por enquanto.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se não tiver nenhum problema, ela volta logo.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.79,0:19:30.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. - OG}Faz sentido.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não dá pra consertar a {\i1}Merry{\i0}?! Por quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.21,0:19:55.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não são carpinteiros navais incríveis?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.38,0:20:00.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you're worried about money, look!\NWe've got tons! - OG}Se o problema é dinheiro, olha!\NTemos de sobra!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It has nothing to do with money. - OG}Dinheiro não é o problema.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.59,0:20:07.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter how much you pay, that ship\Ncan't be restored to how she used to be. - OG}Todo o dinheiro do mundo não pode devolver\No navio de vocês ao estado original.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.31,0:20:15.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm rather impressed that you guys\Nmade it this far in the state she's in. - OG}Aliás, fico surpreso que vocês tenham chegado\Ntão longe num navio nesse estado.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.27,0:20:18.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean?!\NWhat's going on with the Merry? - OG}Como assim?!\NO que há de errado com a {\i1}Merry{\i0}?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you know what a keel is, shameless girl? - OG}Você sabe o que é a quilha, sua sem-vergonha?{Z/WF}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The one at the bottom of the ship? - OG}Aquela parte no fundo do navio?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.49,0:20:27.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right. It's the most\Nimportant wood beam on a ship. - OG}Isso mesmo. É a peça de madeira\Nmais importante do navio.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It crosses from stem to stern and supports the ship. - OG}Ela sustenta o navio da proa à popa.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.04,0:20:35.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando se constrói um navio,\Ncomeça-se colocando a quilha.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then the stem wood, stern wood, and the frame wood— - OG}Depois a proa, a popa\Ne a estrutura—{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.92,0:20:40.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{frame brackets and deck beams... - OG}as cavernas, as aposturas\Ne os vaus do convés...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.80,0:20:45.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We accurately place all those\Npieces of wood around the keel. - OG}E você posiciona cada peça\Nde madeira ao redor da quilha com cuidado.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's how a ship is built. - OG}Construção naval em resumo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.49,0:20:51.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The keel is the very foundation of a ship's framework. It's the essence of the ship. - OG}A quilha é a base fundamental—\Na própria essência—da estrutura de um navio.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.15,0:20:56.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not something you can just replace\Nif it takes on a lot of damage... - OG}Uma vez que esteja danificada além do reparo,\Nnão dá pra simplesmente trocar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.81,0:21:01.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Replacing the keel is the same\Nas building a ship from scratch. - OG}Em outras palavras, trocar a quilha\Né o mesmo que construir um navio do zero.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.03,0:21:04.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, ninguém mais pode consertá-la.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.09,0:21:08.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your ship is just a collection of wood\Nthat can only await her end. - OG}O navio de vocês é pouco mais que\Nsucata de madeira esperando seu fim.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Não fala assim!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Not my problem. That's the truth. - OG}Tanto faz. É a verdade.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.35,0:21:20.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then... Then build a ship from scratch for us! - OG}Então... Então constroem um navio\Ndo zero pra gente!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Construam a {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}!
Comment: 5,0:21:22.89,0:21:25.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Coo coo! }That's not possible either.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso também não é possível.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.19,0:21:26.22,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:26.22,0:21:32.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can build a similar ship, but strictly speaking, no one can build the same ship. - OG}{\q2}Podemos construir um navio parecido, mas sendo sincero,\Nnão seria o mesmo de antes.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.29,0:21:36.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In this world, there are no two ships\Nthat are exactly the same. - OG}A realidade é que dois navios nunca\Npodem ser exatamente iguais.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What does that mean?! - OG}Como assim?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.40,0:21:41.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are there any trees in the world\Nthat grow exactly the same way? - OG}Existem duas árvores no mundo\Nque crescem exatamente do mesmo jeito?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.69,0:21:49.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sailing ships are mostly made of wood, so the size and curves of the ship\Nare all affected by the shape of the trees. - OG}{\q2}Um navio à vela é feito basicamente de madeira, então o tamanho e as curvas\Ndo navio são determinados pelo formato das árvores.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.04,0:21:55.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's why an exact duplicate of the ship can't be built, even when using the same ship's very blueprint. - OG}Por isso, uma réplica exata não pode ser feita,\Nmesmo usando a própria planta do navio.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.29,0:21:58.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{For example, even if we used a blueprint to build such a ship, - OG}Mesmo que seguíssemos uma planta\Npra construir uma cópia,{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.50,0:22:03.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{without a doubt, the ones who would feel\Nthat it's a totally different ship... - OG}a tripulação que melhor conhecia o navio antigo\Ncertamente sentiria a diferença.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:03.39,0:22:05.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{would be you guys! Coo coo! - OG}Essa tripulação seriam {\i1}vocês{\i0}!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, no... - OG}Então, quer dizer...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.47,0:22:13.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then we really can no longer\Ntravel on the Going Merry? - OG}Isso significa que a gente realmente não pode mais\Nnavegar na {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:13.18,0:22:15.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right. - OG}Vocês entenderam a situação.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:15.21,0:22:17.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You either do nothing and wait until she sinks... - OG}Ou navegam com ela até afundar...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.07,0:22:20.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{or you take her apart quickly. - OG}ou a desmontam de uma vez.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.20,0:22:24.27,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma caravela!{Flashback to Syrup Village}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:24.27,0:22:27.36,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a good ship! - OG}Ooh! Que navio incrível!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:28.70,0:22:30.25,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Pronto! Tudo certo!{arch: Match Gaimon at 3:44}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:30.25,0:22:34.17,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now the Going Merry\Npirate ship is all set! - OG}Nosso navio pirata,\Na {\i0}Going Merry{\i1}, está finalmente pronta!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:37.40,0:22:40.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... your ship stands on her last legs. - OG}Bom... o navio de vocês chegou ao fim.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa é uma boa oportunidade.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.18,0:22:44.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just give up and buy a new ship here. - OG}Aceitem a realidade e comprem um navio novo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.49,0:22:48.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've got money, right? I heard that your ship is a caravel. - OG}Vocês têm dinheiro, né? E ouvi\Ncerto que o navio de vocês é uma caravela?{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:49.37,0:22:54.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To start with, your future journeys\Nwill be tough on such an old-style ship. - OG}Pra falar a verdade, é um modelo antigo de navio\Ne não aguentaria a viagem que vem pela frente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:54.34,0:22:56.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não. Eu não pretendo pegar um navio novo.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.80,0:22:58.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:58.30,0:23:00.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nosso...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:00.27,0:23:03.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nosso navio é a {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:03.24,0:23:05.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If she's repaired, she can still sail! - OG}Se for consertada, ela ainda navega!{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.69,0:23:09.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It'll be fine! Today, too,\Nshe sailed here comfortably! - OG}Ela vai ficar bem! Até hoje,\Nela navegou sem nenhum problema!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.32,0:23:12.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And yet, we're suddenly told\Nthat she can't sail anymore...? - OG}E agora, do nada, vocês\Ndizem que ela não pode mais navegar?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:12.49,0:23:14.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can we believe that?! - OG}Quem acreditaria nisso?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.39,0:23:20.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys're saying that because\Nyou don't know how strong she is! - OG}Vocês falam isso porque não sabem\No quanto ela é forte!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:21.28,0:23:23.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Will you be satisfied if you keep\Nsailing on her until she sinks? - OG}Então vocês vão navegar nela até afundar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:23.50,0:23:25.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu Deus.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:26.50,0:23:30.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E você se diz capitão de um navio?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.48,0:23:35.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Our discussion is over for now. Think about it carefully. - OG}Essa discussão acabou.\NPensem bem sobre isso.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.52,0:23:39.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you decide\Nto buy a ship, come again. I'll help you. - OG}Voltem quando estiverem prontos\Npra comprar um navio novo. Eu cuido de vocês.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:39.40,0:23:43.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you give us your 300 million,\Nwe can even build a state-of-the-art ship for you. - OG}Se gastarem os 300 milhões aqui,\Nconstruímos um navio de última geração.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:43.28,0:23:45.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:45.07,0:23:47.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes. Please give it a thought. - OG}Aqui. Por favor, deem uma olhada.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.80,0:23:51.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a catalog that\Ncontains both new and used models. Please use it as a price reference. - OG}Este catálogo lista modelos novos e usados.\NUsem como referência de preços também.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:51.84,0:23:53.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]! - OG}Sr. Iceburg!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:54.32,0:23:57.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's someone at\Nthe gate who wants to see you. - OG}Tem uma visita no portão.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:57.08,0:24:00.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1024.5,1053)}{Looks like that World Government\NOfficial is here again. - OG}Aquele oficial do Governo Mundial\Nvoltou, pelo que parece.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:00.40,0:24:01.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Devo dispensá-lo?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:02.26,0:24:05.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... yeah... Tell him I'm out. - OG}Bom, claro! Diz que eu não tô aqui.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:05.49,0:24:09.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, you've got quite\Na case of bed head, Lulu. - OG}Aliás, esse seu cabelo tá\Numa bagunça, Lulu.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:09.30,0:24:11.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oops. Pardon me. - OG}Eita! Com licença!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:12.13,0:24:14.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, então vou pedir pra ele ir embora.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:14.00,0:24:15.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É-É, pode ser?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:15.61,0:24:18.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera aí, Iceburg{-kun}.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:20.90,0:24:22.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you're around. - OG}Então você está aqui.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:22.85,0:24:26.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you guys, hide!\NIt's a government official! - OG}Ei, vocês, se escondam!\NSão oficiais do governo!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:26.00,0:24:26.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? T-Tá bom.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:32.83,0:24:36.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well... Hi, Corgi. I'm not around today. - OG}Bom, olá, Corgi. Eu não estou aqui hoje.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:36.80,0:24:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, você está!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:38.28,0:24:41.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Seriously, I've come all the way here by sea train. - OG}Olha, eu vim até aqui de Sea Train.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:41.85,0:24:43.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Please don't refuse me. - OG}Por favor, não me evite.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:43.99,0:24:45.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hmm?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:51.80,0:24:55.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I somehow detect the scent of pirates. - OG}Estou sentindo cheiro de piratas.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:55.39,0:24:58.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, that's okay. In any case,\NI want to talk to you. - OG}Tudo bem. Mas eu só vim pra conversar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:58.43,0:25:01.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu te odeio! Vai embora!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:01.10,0:25:02.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you a child? - OG}Que infantilidade.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:02.27,0:25:04.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um homem feito.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:06.90,0:25:09.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, please don't be so obstinate. - OG}Bom, então para de enrolar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:09.08,0:25:13.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I brought a good deal for you today.\NGive me a chance to explain. - OG}Você vai gostar do que eu tenho\Npra dizer. Por favor, só me escute.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:15.53,0:25:18.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, let's go somewhere inconspicuous. - OG}Agora, vamos pra algum lugar reservado.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:20.29,0:25:23.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles ficam voltando. Que insistência.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:23.89,0:25:26.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What business do they have with Iceburg-san? - OG}O que eles querem com o Sr. Iceburg?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:26.19,0:25:30.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem nada a ver com a gente.\NDeve ser coisa de poder.{Coo coo.}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:30.26,0:25:31.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shall I go beat them up? - OG}Quer que eu vá dar uma surra neles?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:31.90,0:25:34.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't. They're from the World Government. - OG}Nem pense nisso.\NSão do Governo Mundial.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:39.01,0:25:39.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:39.68,0:25:41.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? What's the matter? - OG}O quê? O que houve?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:42.60,0:25:46.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is something I noticed when\NI carried these bags and hid earlier...}Eu reparei numa coisa sobre as maletas\Nquando carreguei elas pro esconderijo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:48.40,0:25:50.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They are light, after all. - OG}Elas estão bem leves.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:25:50.10,0:25:52.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como...? Por quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:52.85,0:25:58.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, don't joke like that. Why would they be light with all that money in them? - OG}Ah, para de brincadeira. Não tem como estar\Nleve com todo aquele dinheiro dentro.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:03.66,0:26:05.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are those voices?! - OG}Quem foi que gritou?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:08.00,0:26:10.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus idiotas! Que escândalo é esse?!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:11.05,0:26:14.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, woman! If you sit like that...! - OG}Ei, mulher! Sentada assim dá pra ver...!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:15.28,0:26:18.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que... Não tem...
Dialogue: 5,0:26:20.20,0:26:22.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser...
Dialogue: 5,0:26:24.85,0:26:26.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Our 200 million belly! - OG}Duzentos milhões de belly...!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:26.85,0:26:28.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's gone! It's really gone! - OG}Sumiram! Sumiram de verdade!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:28.81,0:26:32.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{On closer inspection, they're not our bags! - OG}Olhando melhor, essas nem são\Nas nossas maletas!{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:33.23,0:26:34.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O-O-O-O que a gente faz?!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:34.37,0:26:37.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, what are you guys shouting so loud for? - OG}Ei, vocês! Por que tanto gritaria?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:37.32,0:26:40.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nosso dinheiro... sumiu.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:40.40,0:26:43.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele... sumiu... completamente.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:43.29,0:26:44.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:44.21,0:26:45.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Paulie! Did you...? - OG}Paulie! Foi você de novo?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:45.64,0:26:46.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not me! - OG}Não fui eu!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:46.58,0:26:47.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you telling the truth?! - OG}De verdade?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:47.29,0:26:49.10,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Por que eu mentiria?!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:49.10,0:26:49.87,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}É sério mesmo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.87,0:26:50.83,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sério de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.84,0:26:52.42,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mentira. Do nada você tá sério de verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.42,0:27:00.51,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Espera...! Não é...! Só... cala a boca!\NEu juro... não tô mentindo! De verdade!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:49.87,0:26:51.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How noisy... - OG}Eles são tão barulhentos.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:51.51,0:26:55.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{More importantly, Kaku. Weren't you with the Franky Family earlier? - OG}Mais importante, Kaku, eu não vi você\Ncom a Família Franky mais cedo?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:55.79,0:26:57.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? What're you talking about? - OG}Hm? Como assim?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:26:57.70,0:27:00.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I haven't seen the Franky Family today. - OG}Eu não vi a Família Franky\Nem momento nenhum hoje.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:00.51,0:27:05.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's strange. I'm sure I saw your long nose. - OG}Que estranho. Tenho certeza de que vi\Nseu nariz comprido no meio deles.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:05.80,0:27:07.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera aí, gente!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:07.48,0:27:09.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:09.39,0:27:11.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tava com a Família Franky?!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:11.48,0:27:15.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tava com eles, ou melhor,\Nfoi levado por eles.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:15.85,0:27:17.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's an abduction! - OG}Eles sequestraram ele!{To match the new title -gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:17.57,0:27:19.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! We'll go look for him right away! - OG}Luffy! Precisamos achá-lo rápido!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:19.40,0:27:20.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:20.53,0:27:24.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Hold on a sec! Where're you gonna look, Luffy?! - OG}Ei! Espera! Onde você vai procurar, Luffy?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:26.62,0:27:29.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já vou, Usopp! O dinheiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:33.20,0:27:34.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Geez... - OG}Ai, ai...!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:34.41,0:27:37.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, onde fica o esconderijo da Família Franky?
Dialogue: 5,0:27:37.01,0:27:38.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's more like a workshop rather than a hideout, - OG}Não é bem um esconderijo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:38.97,0:27:44.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's more like a workshop rather than a hideout, but it's at the seashore quite a ways northwest from the rocky cape - OG}O lugar é a oficina deles,\Nperto de onde o navio de vocês está ancorado.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:44.09,0:27:47.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{where your ship is anchored. - OG}É só seguir a costa\Na noroeste do Cabo Rochoso.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:27:47.10,0:27:49.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se chama Franky House.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:52.71,0:27:54.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:55.59,0:27:57.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:58.47,0:28:03.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Seriously, when there's no way he\Ncould find Usopp all by himself...! - OG}Que absurdo! Como se ele conseguisse\Nachar o Usopp sozinho!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:03.84,0:28:06.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have no time to look for Luffy. - OG}Achar o Luffy vai ter que esperar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:06.01,0:28:08.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'd better go leave this money at the ship for now. - OG}Vou levar o dinheiro de volta pro navio por enquanto.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:09.36,0:28:14.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I march in saying, "Give me our 200 \Nmillion back" with 100 million on me, I'd be asking them to steal it too. - OG}{\q2}Chegar lá pedindo 200 milhões de volta enquanto carrego\N100 milhões é pedir pra roubarem o resto.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:15.35,0:28:19.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, yagara-chan, please head toward\Nthe bull shop using the shortest route! - OG}Enfim, yagara, por favor vá\Npelo caminho mais rápido até a loja de touros!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:25.60,0:28:28.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna take Zoro and the others\Nwith me and teach them a lesson! - OG}Eu, o Zoro e os outros\Nvamos dar uma lição neles!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:28.56,0:28:33.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Franky Family! Stealing from pirates?! You're the lowest! - OG}Família Franky! Roubar de piratas\Nfoi uma péssima escolha!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:39.52,0:28:43.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is the first floor, the backstreet shopping district. - OG}Bem-vindos ao primeiro nível,\No distrito comercial dos Becos.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:43.81,0:28:46.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se cuidem e tenham um bom dia!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:50.04,0:28:51.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô contando com você, yagara{-chan}!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:54.60,0:28:56.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:56.58,0:28:58.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, cuidado, moça!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:58.75,0:29:00.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:01.71,0:29:05.97,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I hope... Usopp got away okay. - OG}Usopp... Me diz que você conseguiu escapar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:29:19.11,0:29:20.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é horrível.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:20.49,0:29:21.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é esse cara?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:21.79,0:29:24.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Alguém conhece esse cara?!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:24.07,0:29:25.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma multidão...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:25.80,0:29:28.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, yagara{-chan}! Para! Para!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:34.70,0:29:36.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:39.00,0:29:40.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Acorda!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:40.38,0:29:42.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Você tá bem?!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:42.84,0:29:43.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! - OG}Ei!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:29:43.92,0:29:47.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Usopp! Usopp! - OG}Ei! Usopp! Usopp!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:29:47.00,0:29:49.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, are you guys pirates by any chance? - OG}Ei, vocês por acaso\Nsão piratas?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:29:49.83,0:29:52.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up! Don't stare at us! - OG}Cala a boca! Para de ficar olhando!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:29:54.30,0:29:58.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Foi a Família Franky\Nque fez isso com você? Foi?!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:01.49,0:30:05.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah... Because I'm weak. - OG}Foi... Eu era fraco demais.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:06.61,0:30:08.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All that money... - OG}Nosso dinheiro...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:08.30,0:30:10.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{they stole it. - OG}eles levaram tudo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:12.50,0:30:14.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 5,0:30:14.01,0:30:15.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:16.41,0:30:20.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A tripulação... Eu não consigo encará-los.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:24.60,0:30:29.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We were finally about to have Merry repaired... - OG}E... a gente tava tão perto\Nde ter a {\i1}Merry{\i0} consertada.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:31.99,0:30:35.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu me sinto... tão envergonhado.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:37.71,0:30:40.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:41.05,0:30:43.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp, eu entendo.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:43.90,0:30:48.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about the money.\NWe'll all go and get it back for sure. - OG}Não se preocupa com o dinheiro.\NPode contar com a gente pra recuperá-lo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:48.32,0:30:53.08,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's hurt quite badly.\NI probably shouldn't move him. - OG}Ele tá bem machucado.\NMelhor não mexer nele.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:53.70,0:30:56.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp, stay here for a while. - OG}Usopp, fica aqui um pouco.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:30:56.50,0:31:00.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll hurry back to the ship\Nand bring back help. - OG}Eu vou correndo pro navio e volto com ajuda!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:00.30,0:31:02.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu trago o Chopper também\Npra te tratar!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:02.88,0:31:05.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about the stolen money. - OG}Por favor, não se preocupa com o dinheiro!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:05.39,0:31:08.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I heard that their hideout is ahead of here. - OG}Ouvi que o esconderijo deles é logo ali na frente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:08.37,0:31:10.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So we'll crush them and\Nthat'll be the end of them! - OG}A gente vai esmagar eles e acabou!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:12.05,0:31:16.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Isso aqui não é espetáculo!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:16.90,0:31:19.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Listen, Usopp. Just stay here, okay? - OG}Escuta, Usopp. Só fica aqui, tá?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:20.40,0:31:22.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll be back right away! - OG}Eu já volto!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:26.94,0:31:30.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go faster, yagara-chan! - OG}Mais rápido, yagara!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:32.99,0:31:35.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! Um touro descontrolado!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:34.89,0:31:35.58,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:37.62,0:31:42.29,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{We were finally about to have Merry repaired... - OG}E... a gente tava tão perto\Nde ter a Merry consertada.{Flashback to: same episode, timestamp 30:24}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:44.04,0:31:48.71,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter how much you pay, that ship\Ncan't be restored to how she used to be. - OG}Todo o dinheiro do mundo não pode devolver\No navio de vocês ao estado original.{Flashback to: same episode, timestamp 20:02}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:49.80,0:31:53.47,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Quer a gente decida comprar um navio novo...
Dialogue: 5,0:31:53.47,0:31:57.39,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{or have someone else manage to fix\Nand improve the Merry, - OG}ou ache alguém disposto a\Nconsertar e melhorar a {\i1}Merry{\i0},{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:31:57.39,0:32:01.89,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{unless we spend the entire 300 million\Nto upgrade or get a new ship– - Z}temos que gastar todos os 300 milhões\Npra melhorar ou comprar um navio novo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:01.89,0:32:04.23,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{our future journey will certainly be hard. - OG}{our next journey is over before it starts. - Z}Os mares só vão ficar mais perigosos daqui pra frente.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:05.34,0:32:07.99,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente precisa desse dinheiro com certeza.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:07.99,0:32:09.69,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have to get it back without fail! - OG}A gente {\i1}tem{\i0} que recuperar ele!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:12.70,0:32:14.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é verdade?!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:14.28,0:32:17.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos foi o que aquele carpinteiro disse.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:19.29,0:32:20.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse navio...
Dialogue: 5,0:32:20.58,0:32:23.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...can no longer be fixed?\NEven if we pay lots of money?! - OG}...não pode mais ser consertado?\NMesmo que a gente tenha dinheiro?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:23.50,0:32:26.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then... What's gonna happen to the Merry?! - OG}Então, o que vai acontecer com a {\i1}Merry{\i0}?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:26.46,0:32:27.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sei lá.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:27.91,0:32:32.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In the end, it depends on how Luffy\Nand the others decide after hearing the outcome of the assessment. - OG}No final, tudo depende de como o Luffy,\Na Nami e o Usopp vão reagir à avaliação.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:33.60,0:32:37.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Those three at the shipyard\Nwill probably make some decision. - OG}Aqueles três no estaleiro provavelmente\Nvão encontrar uma solução.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:37.60,0:32:40.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That doesn't sound right.\NIt's too extreme. - OG}Não acredito nisso. Parece muito repentino.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:40.89,0:32:44.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha pro navio! É a mesma {\i1}Merry{\i0} de sempre.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:44.10,0:32:48.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We and Merry traveled together all\Nthe way here from the East Blue! - OG}Do East Blue até aqui,\Na gente ficou com a {\i1}Merry{\i0} o caminho todo!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:48.65,0:32:51.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's exactly why, right? - OG}Mas é exatamente por isso.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:51.49,0:32:54.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{While humans who've endured\Nhardship become more resilient, - Z}Humanos enfrentam dificuldades\Ne ficam mais resistentes;{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:55.05,0:32:56.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but ships are different. - OG}navios são diferentes.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:32:56.70,0:32:59.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Their pain only accumulates. - OG}Eles acumulam desgaste e dano.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:03.85,0:33:05.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É difícil de engolir.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:05.54,0:33:09.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Besides, what's Usopp\Ngonna say when he hears it? - OG}Além disso, como o Usopp vai reagir\Nquando souber disso?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:09.10,0:33:11.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eu amo a {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:11.61,0:33:16.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We all do. But like that guy said,\Nher battle scars are too deep. - OG}Todos nós amamos. Mas como aquele cara disse,\Nas cicatrizes de batalha dela são profundas demais.{Z}{Flashback to: same episode, timestamp 17:07}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:18.75,0:33:21.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem a {\i1}Going Merry{\i0},\Nmas também tem a Robin{-chan}.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:22.43,0:33:24.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a restless afternoon... - OG}Que tarde deprimente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:26.11,0:33:27.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:30.25,0:33:32.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh? A Nami voltou!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:32.36,0:33:35.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm? Parece que ela tá sozinha.
Dialogue: 5,0:33:35.10,0:33:37.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com o Luffy e o Usopp?
Dialogue: 5,0:33:37.81,0:33:41.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}! Aconteceu alguma coisa?!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:45.75,0:33:49.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai! Ai, ai!\NVocê disse "200 milhões"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:49.69,0:33:51.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, 200 milhões!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:51.59,0:33:54.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you, Bro?! - OG}O que acha, Mano?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:54.51,0:33:57.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Incredible! You guys are amazing! - OG}Incrível! Vocês são demais!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:33:57.89,0:34:03.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've always wanted that.\NWith this much money, we can finally get it! - OG}Com toda essa grana, finalmente podemos\Nconseguir o que a gente sempre quis!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:03.39,0:34:05.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos, né, Mano?
Dialogue: 5,0:34:05.49,0:34:09.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Three years of persevering...\NWe've always said, "If only we could get it..." - OG}Depois de três longos anos!\NVocê sempre dizia: "Quando eu tiver a grana..."{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:09.13,0:34:11.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{– It was such a long time.\N– Yeah. - OG}– Demorou tanto.\N– É.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:11.02,0:34:15.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cada vez que juntávamos uma grana,\Na gente apostava em corridas de yagara...
Dialogue: 5,0:34:15.39,0:34:16.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...and lose all the money! - OG}– ...e ficávamos sem nada!\N– ...e ficávamos sem nada!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:16.90,0:34:20.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cada vez que capturávamos um criminoso\Ncom recompensa, a gente fazia uma festa...
Dialogue: 5,0:34:20.60,0:34:22.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...and lose all the money! - OG}– ...e ficávamos sem nada!\N– ...e ficávamos sem nada!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:22.16,0:34:27.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nunca conseguimos juntar\Nos 200 milhões de belly necessários!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:27.21,0:34:29.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But we finally have it now! - OG}Mas finalmente conseguimos!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:29.13,0:34:33.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah!\NGood job, you guys! - OG}Isso aí! Vocês se superaram, galera!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:33.84,0:34:38.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well then, this isn't much,\Nbut here is five million belly. - OG}Bom, não é muito,\Nmas aqui vão cinco milhões de belly.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:38.51,0:34:42.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is to show my appreciation.\NEat and drink as you please! - OG}É pra mostrar minha gratidão.\NComam, bebam e aproveitem!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:34:46.30,0:34:48.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o nosso Mano!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:48.01,0:34:49.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É hora da festa!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:57.01,0:34:58.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:34:59.80,0:35:00.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:35:01.20,0:35:02.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit!}Ah, droga!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:02.70,0:35:07.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who's trying to defy the Franky Family?! - OG}Quem é você?! Quer encarar\Na Família Franky?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:13.09,0:35:16.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Huh?! You're that weak guy from earlier! - OG}Hã?! Você é aquele magrelo de antes!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:16.61,0:35:18.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? You could still stand? - OG}Como é que ainda tá de pé?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:22.30,0:35:24.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give me the money back! - OG}Me devolvam o dinheiro!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:24.01,0:35:30.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"Give me the money back"?\NThen are you one of the Straw Hat's underlings? - OG}"Me devolvam o dinheiro"?\NEntão, você é um dos capangas do Chapéu de Palha?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:31.31,0:35:33.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo, Mano!
Dialogue: 5,0:35:33.56,0:35:39.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como ele tá com o Chapéu de Palha Luffy,\Na gente esperava um pirata durão...
Dialogue: 5,0:35:39.01,0:35:41.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's so weak! - OG}...mas no final é só um fracote!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:41.92,0:35:44.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's none of your business! - OG}Como se vocês entendessem alguma coisa!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:45.62,0:35:46.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oops! - OG}Epa!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:51.61,0:35:53.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's he doing?! - OG}Ele tá falando sério?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:35:53.04,0:35:56.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Admito que você tem coragem de vir\Nsozinho atrás do dinheiro,
Dialogue: 5,0:35:56.81,0:35:59.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I can't let you have it back. - OG}mas eu não posso devolver.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:02.91,0:36:04.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give it back to me! - OG}Me devolve!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:04.89,0:36:11.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente precisa... consertar nosso navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:36:14.48,0:36:17.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That money is crucial to us! - OG}Precisamos desesperadamente desse dinheiro!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:21.49,0:36:25.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com esse dinheiro, a gente finalmente...
Dialogue: 5,0:36:25.08,0:36:30.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We can finally repair the Going Merry's scars! - OG}Finalmente pode curar as feridas\Nda {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:30.62,0:36:35.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't let you jerks have it! - OG}Esse dinheiro... eu não vou deixar vocês ficarem com ele!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:41.68,0:36:43.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are you so worked up about? - OG}Por que tanto desespero?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:44.50,0:36:48.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Looks like you love your ship quite a bit. - OG}Pelo visto você ama mesmo seu navio.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:48.19,0:36:52.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well! No matter what happens to your ship, - OG}Bom! Não importa o que aconteça\Ncom o navio de vocês.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:52.64,0:36:56.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{this money is already ours. - OG}Esse dinheiro agora é {\i1}nosso{\i0}.{Z - Used as flashback in Water Seven 6 @16:24}
Dialogue: 5,0:36:58.52,0:37:04.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Infelizmente pra você, ninguém considera\Nroubar de piratas um crime.{OG}{Unfortunately for you, no one considers\Nstealing from pirates a crime. - Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:04.09,0:37:07.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is dirty money that you stole\Nfrom somewhere anyway, right? - OG}Deixa eu adivinhar! É dinheiro sujo\Nque vocês roubaram por aí, né?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:09.00,0:37:11.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, let us have it. - OG}Então, deixa com a gente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:13.21,0:37:16.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you like, try begging the Marines for help. - OG}Você pode sempre implorar ajuda dos Marinheiros.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:16.67,0:37:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys are the ones who'll be captured. - OG}Mas vocês é que vão ser presos.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:20.81,0:37:23.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Too bad for Straw Hat Luffy... - OG}É uma pena que o Chapéu de Palha Luffy...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:23.61,0:37:29.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{that he has a useless underling\Nwho can't even watch over money. - OG}tenha um capanga tão inútil\Nque nem consegue guardar o dinheiro.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:37.10,0:37:41.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Guys, have some fun with him later. - OG}Galera, divirtam-se com ele depois.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:42.57,0:37:47.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna take this money\Nand go shopping at once. - OG}Agora eu vou pegar essa grana\Ne fazer umas comprinhas!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:48.06,0:37:49.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is gonna be great! - OG}Mal posso esperar!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:49.53,0:37:50.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hold it! - OG}Espera aí!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:50.49,0:37:53.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:00.75,0:38:05.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lembre-se disso, garoto do nariz comprido.\NMeu nome é Franky.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:05.72,0:38:11.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you want to leave this town alive,\Nyou shouldn't cross me. - OG}Se quer sair dessa cidade vivo,\Né melhor nunca se meter comigo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:38:14.60,0:38:18.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê... O que vocês estão fazendo?! Me larga!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:22.51,0:38:26.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Such a pathetic weapon wouldn't work on us. - OG}Uma arma ridícula dessas não funciona com a gente!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:38:26.95,0:38:29.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Até logo, narigudo.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:29.28,0:38:32.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Valeu pelos 200 milhões de belly.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:32.79,0:38:36.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hold it! Give it back... to me! - OG}Espera! Me devolve... isso!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:38:36.10,0:38:37.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me devolve!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:38.10,0:38:39.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me devoooolve!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:49.29,0:38:50.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me... devolve.
Dialogue: 5,0:38:50.97,0:38:53.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me... devoooolve!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:05.44,0:39:08.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me... de... volve!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:10.87,0:39:15.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me devooooooolve!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:24.73,0:39:27.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu só preciso aguentar\Naté a Robin voltar.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:30.43,0:39:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll only become a burden to them\Nif I march in with them. - OG}Eu só ia atrapalhar se fosse\Njunto com os outros.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:39:34.51,0:39:35.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It'll be scary, too. - OG}E tô com medo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:39:37.59,0:39:42.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At any rate, I'll protect this ship\Nand the 100 million belly all the way. - OG}De qualquer forma, eu vou proteger\Nesse navio e os 100 milhões de belly custe o que custar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:39:42.10,0:39:44.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm counting on you... - OG}O resto fica nas mãos de vocês...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:39:44.27,0:39:45.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{guys! - OG}galera!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:39:47.04,0:39:49.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para. Para!
Dialogue: 5,0:39:52.71,0:39:57.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se não me engano, aqui deve ser\No lugar que a Nami{-san} falou.
Dialogue: 5,0:39:59.69,0:40:02.38,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Look. This is the backstreet shopping district. - OG}Olha. Aqui é o distrito comercial dos Becos.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:40:02.38,0:40:07.60,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Você sobe por esse canal... e aqui!\NO Usopp tá bem aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:07.60,0:40:08.93,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:08.93,0:40:13.20,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,E aí, Nami{-san}, onde a gente encontra esses\Ndesmontadores, a Família Franky?
Dialogue: 5,0:40:14.60,0:40:16.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:16.00,0:40:17.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He isn't here? - OG}O Usopp não tá aqui?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:40:17.21,0:40:19.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you sure? Didn't you just\Nscrew up the directions? - OG}Tem certeza? Será que você não\Nerrou o caminho.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:40:19.80,0:40:21.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not you! Keep your mouth shut! - OG}Olha quem fala, espadaburro!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:40:21.77,0:40:23.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:23.40,0:40:26.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{– What'd you say?!\N– Ah, look at that! - OG}– O que você disse?!\N– Ah!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:29.50,0:40:31.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha! É sangue!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:31.28,0:40:34.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That idiot! He just walked off\Nwithout waiting for us! - OG}Aquele idiota! Saiu andando\Nsem esperar a gente!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:40:34.82,0:40:37.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me he... - OG}{Do you really think he...? - Z}Ele não pode ter feito isso, né?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:40:37.63,0:40:39.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp.
Dialogue: 5,0:40:40.69,0:40:47.25,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ahhh...
Dialogue: 5,0:40:42.08,0:40:43.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:40:47.25,0:40:48.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...ahhh!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:54.30,0:40:55.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me ajuda!
Dialogue: 5,0:40:55.56,0:40:57.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:03.82,0:41:07.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você tá fazendo?!\NDe onde você caiu?
Dialogue: 5,0:41:08.85,0:41:10.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do estaleiro...
Dialogue: 5,0:41:10.20,0:41:14.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was jumping around imitating this\None shipwright to look for Usopp. - OG}Eu tava imitando aquele carpinteiro,\Npulando por aí pra procurar o Usopp.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:41:14.28,0:41:15.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:41:15.45,0:41:16.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:16.82,0:41:19.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade, pessoal! Temos um problema!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:19.56,0:41:21.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp got abducted, along with the money. - OG}O Usopp foi levado junto com o dinheiro!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:41:22.31,0:41:23.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, a gente sabe.
Dialogue: 5,0:41:23.93,0:41:27.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come on. We're on our way to their hideout. - OG}Vem. A gente tá indo pro esconderijo deles.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:41:27.96,0:41:30.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp got beaten up\Nand had the money stolen from him. - OG}Eles bateram no Usopp\Ne roubaram o dinheiro.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:41:30.70,0:41:31.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:41:33.60,0:41:35.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's possible that he felt responsible... - OG}Talvez ele tenha se culpado...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:41:35.53,0:41:40.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and went to pick a fight\Nwith the Franky Family all by himself. - OG}e foi sozinho enfrentar\Na Família Franky.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:42:02.41,0:42:04.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá respirando, Chopper?
Dialogue: 5,0:42:04.89,0:42:07.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Although he's completely unconscious, - OG}Ele perdeu a consciência...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:42:07.30,0:42:09.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{he's still alive. - OG}mas ainda tá vivo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:42:09.09,0:42:11.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele vai ficar bem. Eu consigo salvá-lo.
Dialogue: 5,0:42:16.49,0:42:18.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just wait a bit... - OG}Só descansa um pouco...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:42:18.76,0:42:20.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp.
Dialogue: 5,0:42:44.31,0:42:48.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna go blow that stupid house away! - OG}A gente vai demolir aquela casa estúpida.{Z/Gaijin}
